trans-unit.source: The Azure Diagnostics configuration file defines values that are used to initialize the Diagnostics Monitor.
trans-unit.target: The Azure Diagnostics configuration file defines values that are used to initialize the Diagnostics Monitor.

trans-unit.source: This file is used to initialize diagnostic configuration settings when the diagnostics monitor starts.
trans-unit.target: This file is used to initialize diagnostic configuration settings when the diagnostics monitor starts.

trans-unit.source: By default, the Azure Diagnostics configuration schema file is installed to the <codeInline>C:\Program Files\Microsoft SDKs\Azure\.NET SDK\%%amp;lt;version%%amp;gt;\schemas</codeInline> directory.
trans-unit.target: By default, the Azure Diagnostics configuration schema file is installed to the <codeInline>C:\Program Files\Microsoft SDKs\Azure\.NET SDK\%%amp;lt;version%%amp;gt;\schemas</codeInline> directory.

trans-unit.source: Replace <codeInline>%%amp;lt;version%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the installed version of the <externalLink><linkText>Azure SDK</linkText><linkUri>http://www.windowsazure.com/develop/downloads/</linkUri></externalLink>.
trans-unit.target: Replace <codeInline>%%amp;lt;version%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the installed version of the <externalLink><linkText>Azure SDK</linkText><linkUri>http://www.windowsazure.com/develop/downloads/</linkUri></externalLink>.

trans-unit.source: The diagnostics configuration file is typically used with startup tasks that require diagnostic data to be collected earlier in the startup process.
trans-unit.target: The diagnostics configuration file is typically used with startup tasks that require diagnostic data to be collected earlier in the startup process.

trans-unit.source: For more information about using Azure Diagnostics, see <legacyLink xlink:href="83a91c23-5ca2-4fc9-8df3-62036c37a3d7" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Collect Logging Data by Using Azure Diagnostics</legacyLink>.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the interval at which the diagnostic monitor polls for diagnostic configuration changes.
